author: More Perfect Union
description:
Nearly 5 million people in Florida get their health care through Obamacare plans.

But the cost of these plans is set to skyrocket in 2026 when federal subsidies expire.

We spoke with Republican voters — including a resident who was quoted a 291% increase in her premium.
